OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment weighs up 6.5%  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpublic sector pay increase 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is considering pay      
OL,6, increases of between 6%-6.5% for public
OL,7, sector workers, the BBC understands.   
OL,9,FOfficial pay review bodies for         
OL,10,Femployees including teachers, junior   
OL,11,Fdoctors and police have recommended the
OL,12,Fpay rise. Inflation to May was 8.7%.   
OL,14,FThe prime minister and chancellor are  
OL,15,Fexpected to meet this week or next to  
OL,16,Fdecide whether to accept the rises.    
OL,18,FGovernment sources have told the BBC   
OL,19,Fany rises over 3.5% would need to come 
OL,20,Fout of existing departmental budgets.  
